 Available experimental data were interpreted  using              5846 1451
 nuclear reaction model code EMPIRE-2.19b31 by                    5846 1451
 M. Herman et al [He01, He02]. This code integrates               5846 1451
 into a single system a number of important modules               5846 1451
 and features:                                                    5846 1451
                                                                  5846 1451
 - Spherical and deformed Optical Model including                 5846 1451
   coupled-channels (ECIS03 by J. Raynal)                         5846 1451
 - Hauser-Feshbach statistical model including                    5846 1451
   HRTW width fluctuation correction                              5846 1451
 - Quantum-mechanical MSD TUL model (codes ORION &                5846 1451
   TRISTAN by H. Lenske), and MSC NVWY model                      5846 1451
